window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Immortality comes at a steep price.</b></p> <p>Faced with a heartrending loss, Lox walks down a dark path. He knew there would be a cost for immortality, but he didn’t know he would have to face it so soon.</p> <p>He must make decisions he never thought he would face.&nbsp;</p> <p>A darkness is lingering in the world. Maybe what it needs right now isn’t a hero to save it, but a monster to hunt the bigger monsters threatening all of existence.</p> <p>Rage guides Lox's path. But will that be enough to hold off the coming darkness? Or will consume him first?</p> <p><b>Don't miss this epic LitRPG/GameLit series that features leveling, advanced magic systems, dungeon crawling, world exploration, and much more. It's perfect for fans of books like </b><b><i>Emarilia, World Tree</i></b><b>, and </b><b><i>Ascend Online</i></b><b>.</b></p>"; 
